## Fixes Applied in This Session

### Fix 1: Main Application Package → Moved to `com.ticketing`
The class is being moved and `application.yaml` is populated below.

### Fix 2: `application.yaml` and `application-local.yml` Created

**`application.yaml`** (base — profile pointer only):
```yaml
spring:
  application:
    name: ticketing-platform
  profiles:
    active: local
```

**`application-local.yml`** (local Docker dev):
```yaml
spring:
  datasource:
    url: jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/ticketing_db
    username: ticketing
    password: ticketing
    driver-class-name: org.postgresql.Driver
  data:
    redis:
      host: localhost
      port: 6379
  rabbitmq:
    host: localhost
    port: 5672
    username: ticketing
    password: ticketing
  flyway:
    enabled: true
    locations: classpath:db/migration

logging:
  level:
    com.ticketing: DEBUG
    org.springframework.security: INFO
```

### Fix 3: `copilot-instructions.md` — Stack versions corrected
Line 9 updated to: `PostgreSQL 17, Redis 7, RabbitMQ 4.2.5`

### Fix 4: `intsructions.txt` line 114 and `day-01-project-init.md` line 94 updated
`qrgen 2.6.0` → `com.google.zxing:core:3.5.2 + com.google.zxing:javase:3.5.2`

